0x9743BCCF7CD6E1F6// HasScaleformMovieNamedLoaded
BOOL _HAS_SCALEFORM_MOVIE_NAMED_LOADED(int* scaleformHandle, char* scaleformName);Parameters:scaleformHandle: Scaleform movie handlescaleformName: Name of the Scaleform movie to checkReturns: Returns true if the named Scaleform movie is loaded, false otherwise.Check if a Scaleform movie with the given name has been loaded.NativeDB Introduced: v3407
